    "causal_summary": "The SpecKit slash-command directory was named `spec_kit/` (snake_case with underscore), inconsistent with the recent rename convention shipping `speckit` (single token) across the repo — e.g., `/create:sk-skill → /create:skill` and `doctor/help.md → doctor/speckit.md`. The directory name drives the slash-command form, so every `/spec_kit:plan`, `/spec_kit:complete`, etc. invocation was misaligned with the canonical short form.",
